## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [SALK_147329]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Abnormal accumulation of storage protein precursors including 17 kDa pro2S albumin in heterozygous seed (homozygous seed does not germinate).
   - [mip2-1 mip3-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Shorter root and delayed development. Accumulation of seed storage protein precursors. Smaller seed, lower thousand-grain weight and lower protein content, severe ER stress, decreased germination ratio with increased storage time, sensitive to ABA and salt stress, ABA signaling pathway affected.
